courses.customDesc: Select one of the following: AEPS150, AEPS190, AEPS250, AEPS260.

One course from each of the following GE areas must be completed: A1, A2, A3, B1, C1, C2, C3, C4, C1-C5 elective, D1, D2, D3, and D5. C4 should be taken only after Junior standing is reached (90 units). Teaching candidates are advised to take KINE 250 (D4). One (1) course must be completed from B1, in addition to MATH 118. Refer to online catalog for GE course selection and Graduation Writing Requirement (GWR) requirements.
